== 影响 ==
總統特朗普于美东时间2017年1月27日签署、颁布这项行政命令之后，美国边境口岸的官员就迅速开始执行这项新规。据《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》报道，来自受影响国家的不同背景和不同身份的公民，要么被拒绝入关、要么被遣返回国；其中包括[[难民|难民]]和来自受影响国家的[[基督徒|基督徒]]等，以及[[学生|学生]]和从海外回美的[[绿卡|绿卡]]持有者<ref name=nyt_impact>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/28/us/refugees-detained-at-us-airports-prompting-legal-challenges-to-trumps-immigration-order.html |title=Judge Blocks Part of Trump's Immigration Order |last=Shear |first=Michael D. |date=2017-01-28 |last2=Feuer |first2=Alan |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |accessdate=2017-01-29 |archive-date=2017-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128170624/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/28/us/refugees-detained-at-us-airports-prompting-legal-challenges-to-trumps-immigration-order.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=cnn20170129>{{cite news |last1=Jorgensen |first1=Sarah |title=Syrian Christian family, visas in hand, turned back at airport |url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/28/us/syrian-family-trump-travel-ban/ |accessdate=2017-01-29 |work=CNN |publisher=Turner Broadcasting System |date=2017-01-29 |archive-date=2017-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129031642/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/28/us/syrian-family-trump-travel-ban/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=abc20170129>{{Cite news |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/trumps-immigration-order-sparks-protests-airports-nationwide/story?id=45119839 |title=Trump's Immigration Order Sparks Protests at Airports Nationwide |last=Jacobo |first=Julia |date=2017-01-29 |work=ABC News |access-date=2017-01-29 |via= |archive-date=2020-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217124953/https://abcnews.go.com/US/trumps-immigration-order-sparks-protests-airports-nationwide/story?id=45119839 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至1月29日，已经有至少375名赴美人士受到了新政的影响<ref name=nyt_impact/><ref name=cnn20170129/><ref name=abc20170129/>。

受限国家的公民无法登机前往美国，就算持有合法有效的[[签证|签证]]也无济于事，有些乘客因为美国的新政而滞留在进行[[转机|转机]]的第三国<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/28/politics/donald-trump-executive-order-immigration-reaction/index.html |title=Trump's immigration ban sends shockwaves |first1=Jeremy |last1=Diamond |first2=Steve |last2=Almasy |publisher=CNN |accessdate=January 29, 2017 |archive-date=2017-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201203043/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/28/politics/donald-trump-executive-order-immigration-reaction/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦有一些乘客正在飞往美国的途中，但与此同时由于行政命令作為法律开始生效，在抵达美国后即被拘留。1月28日，[[美国公民自由联盟|美国公民自由联盟]]（ACLU）估测约有100至200人在全美各大机场被拘留<ref name="BBC News JFK Airport 2017">{{cite web |title=Trump executive order: Refugees detained at US airports |publisher=BBC News |date=January 28, 2017 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-38783512 |accessdate=January 28, 2017 |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310010235/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-38783512 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，还有数百人被拒绝登上赴美班机<ref name=abc_numbers>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/detained-york-airport-cairo-wake-trumps-executive-order/story?id=45109972 |title=Protests Spread at Airports Nationwide Over Trump's Executive Order |publisher=ABC News |date=January 28, 2017 |access-date=2017-01-31 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308141605/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/detained-york-airport-cairo-wake-trumps-executive-order/story?id=45109972 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，还有约60名拥有永久居留权的居民，据报道在[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]附近的[[华盛顿杜勒斯国际机场|华盛顿杜勒斯国际机场]]被拘留<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-29/u-s-entry-ban-from-seven-muslim-countries-causing-alarm-anger |title=Judges Block Parts of Trump's Order on Muslim Nation Immigration |last=Wadhams |first=Nick |date=January 29, 2017 |last2=Sink |first2=Justin |newspaper=Bloomberg |last3=Palmeri |first3=Christopher |last4=Van Voris |first4=Bob |accessdate=January 29, 2017 |archive-date=2017-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129041458/https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-29/u-s-entry-ban-from-seven-muslim-countries-causing-alarm-anger |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但[[美国国土安全部|美国国土安全部]]表示，1月28日的行政命令，在所有抵达美国本土的325000人中，仅仅影响了其中的不到百分之一。截至1月29日，国土安全部估计有109名旅客在转机过程中受到了影响<ref name="foxnews">{{cite news|title=Federal judge grants stay to allow those with visas to remain|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2017/01/29/federal-judge-grants-stay-to-allow-those-with-visas-to-remain.html|accessdate=2017-01-29|agency=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|publisher=[[FOX_NEWS|FOX NEWS]]|date=2017-01-29|archive-date=2018-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180419151258/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2017/01/29/federal-judge-grants-stay-to-allow-those-with-visas-to-remain.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外还有173名旅客被拒绝登机。亦有媒体报道，在美国一些机场，口岸警卫已经开始要求入境旅客上报社交网站的账号。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theverge.com/2017/1/30/14438280/trump-border-agents-search-social-media-instagram |title=Trump's executive order spurs Facebook and Twitter checks at the border |last=Brandom |first=Russell |date=30 January 2017 |work=The Verge |access-date=30 January 2017 |via= |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309014401/https://www.theverge.com/2017/1/30/14438280/trump-border-agents-search-social-media-instagram |dead-url=no }}</ref>

